F_1\subset F_2
\mathbb{E}X^2 < \infty
\mathbb{E}|X-\mathbb{E}(X|F_2)|^2 \le \mathbb{E}|X-\mathbb{E}(X|F_1)|^2 
Y:=X-\mathbb{E}(X|F_1)
\mathbb{E}(|Y-\mathbb{E}(Y|F_2)|^2|F_2) \le \mathbb{E}(Y^2|F_2)
